Album: KamikazeThe Ringer"The Ringer" is a song by American rapper Eminem from his album Kamikaze (2018). It debuted in the top 10 in Australia, Canada, Finland, Ireland, New Zealand, Norway, Portugal, Sweden, Switzerland, the United Kingdom, and the United States. It contains an interpolation from "Ooouuu", written by Matthew Jacobson and Katorah Marrero, as performed by Young M.A.Greatest
